metadata.name: Captain’s Log, Sea date # 42
metadata.description:
Somewhere mid Atlantic. Black waters glitch in the crescent moon. Inching towards Manhattan. Plans to arrive for XCOPY auction long canceled by Gods of the wind

A lone whale circles. Or maybe more. It’s hard to tell. I’ve not rested in many nights
